---
layout: layout.njk
title: Home
---

<section class="hero" style="background-image: url('/images/hero.jpg');">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Discover Europe's Hidden Gems on a Budget</h1>
    <p>Join us as we explore the lesser-known destinations across Europe without breaking the bank.</p>
    <a href="#destinations" class="btn">Start Exploring</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="destinations" class="featured-destinations">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Featured Destinations</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/destination1.jpg" alt="Destination 1">
        <h3>Destination 1</h3>
        <p>Brief description of Destination 1.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/destination2.jpg" alt="Destination 2">
        <h3>Destination 2</h3>
        <p>Brief description of Destination 2.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <img src="/images/destination3.jpg" alt="Destination 3">
        <h3>Destination 3</h3>
        <p>Brief description of Destination 3.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="posts" class="latest-posts">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Latest Blog Posts</h2>
    <div class="grid">
      {% for post in collections.post | slice(0, 3) %}
      <div class="post-card">
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(120, true, '...') }}</p>
        <p class="meta">ðŸ“… {{ post.date | date("MMMM dd, yyyy") }}</p>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="about" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>About Us</h2>
    <p>We are an Egyptian couple passionate about uncovering Europe's hidden gems. Our mission is to provide budget-friendly travel guides, tips, and stories to inspire your next adventure.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Have questions or want to collaborate? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:contact@bucketlessadventures.com">contact@bucketlessadventures.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>
